snippet.title: Tokimeki Memorial 2 Taisen Puzzle-Dama
snippet.description:
Now it's time for the sequel. No changes in gameplay or story really. Other than different characters that's really about it.

Past me did you really picked her?! I can't tolerate this!! I'll exact my revenge!
